Invocation Name: finish the phrase
des:
Test your knowledge of famous sayings with the 'Finish the Phrase' game! Finish five new sayings, slogans, idioms, axioms, puns, proverbs, epithets, and clichés each day to conquer the art of adages. How many of these phrases can you finish?

Got feedback? Email finishthephrase@gmail.com
